oices\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"/><div class=\"absolute top-3 left-3 bg-surface/90 px-3 py-1\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[10px] text-primary uppercase tracking-widest\">DAY 3</span></div></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl text-on-surface mb-2\">Critical Choices</h3><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-on-surface/40 uppercase tracking-widest\">Progress</span><span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-primary\">85%</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-on-surface/40 uppercase tracking-widest\">Characters</span><span class=\"text-xs text-on-surface/60\">Ticket Taker, Doctor, Pierrot, Harlequin</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-on-surface/40 uppercase tracking-widest\">Key Events</span><span class=\"text-xs text-on-surface/60\">Relationship Branches, Hidden Events, Ending Flags</span></div></div><span class=\"text-primary font-mono text-xs uppercase hover:underline\">Continue →</span></div></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\" id=\"route-guides\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-primary uppercase tracking-widest\">Route Guides</h2><span class=\"text-primary\">★★★★</span></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/walkthroughs/pierrot-main-route\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Pierrot Route</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Melancholic clown. Memory loops &amp; silence mechanics.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Difficulty: <!-- -->Hard</span></a><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/walkthroughs/doctor-memory-route\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Doctor Route</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Circus physician. Medical files &amp; mirror connections.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Difficulty: <!-- -->Very Hard</span></a><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/walkthroughs/harlequin-true-route\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Harlequin Route</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Chaotic performer. Fractured identity &amp; hidden scenes.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Difficulty: <!-- -->Medium</span></a><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/walkthroughs/null-route\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Secret Route</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Null route. Corrupted files &amp; unused endings.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Difficulty: <!-- -->Extreme</span></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\" id=\"ending-guides\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-primary uppercase tracking-widest\">Ending Guides</h2><span class=\"text-primary\">★★★★</span></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/endings/the-grand-finale\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Good Ending</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Standard completion. Available on first playthrough.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Requires: <!-- -->Any route completion</span></a><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/endings\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Bad Ending</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Fail states &amp; early deaths. Multiple variations.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Requires: <!-- -->Miss key choices</span></a><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/endings/columbinas-truth\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">True Ending</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Requires all routes &amp; hidden flags.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Requires: <!-- -->100% completion</span></a><a class=\"glass-card p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/endings/corrupted-data\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Secret Ending</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm mb-3\">Datamined content. Unused in current build.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[9px] text-secondary uppercase tracking-widest\">Requires: <!-- -->Modified files</span></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\" id=\"hidden-content\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-primary uppercase tracking-widest\">Hidden Content</h2><span class=\"text-primary\">★★★</span></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4\"><div class=\"glass-card p-5 border-l-2 border-l-primary\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">Hidden Dialogue</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/50 text-xs\">Unused voice lines &amp; cut scenes</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 border-l-2 border-l-primary\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">Mirror Breaking</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/50 text-xs\">33-click trigger &amp; reversed audio</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 border-l-2 border-l-primary\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">Pink Ticket</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/50 text-xs\">Color changes &amp; sanity mechanics</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 border-l-2 border-l-primary\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">Missable Events</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/50 text-xs\">Time-gated &amp; failure-locked scenes</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-5 border-l-2 border-l-primary\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-sm text-on-surface mb-1\">Achievements</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/50 text-xs\">Secret badges &amp; completion rewards</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-10\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl text-primary uppercase tracking-widest\">Quick Tips</h2><span class=\"text-primary\">★★★</span></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Beginner Tips</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm\">Save before every major choice. Talk to everyone twice.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Missable Choices</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm\">Some options only appear on specific days or routes.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Relationship Tips</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm\">Character affinity affects ending availability.</p></div><div class=\"glass-card p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg text-on-surface mb-2\">Best Save Points</h3><p class=\"text-on-surface/60 text-sm\">Day 1 Cafe, Day 2 Mirror, Day 3 Decision.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-8\">